{"tid":508533,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"告別單身好機會！香港大型速配跑步","createTime":"2017-12-24T10:52:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T04:05:08.000Z","uid":28366,"like":4,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b5b97e41ab5c91722b37b6d89dc0f3e6be109e2e","tid":508533,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T10:52:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">日期:\t2018年2月11日 9am - 2:30pm<br />\n地點:\t白石角科學園會議中心\t</span><br />\n<br />\n每逢節日，街上情侶一對對，想脫離單身族又熱愛運動的話，不妨參加Run Date 2018，在跑步活動中尋找另一半。情侶亦可以情侶組參加，透過活動增進感情。<br />\n<br />\n今屆Run Date 由本地創意媒體 Honkiee及交友平台Coffee Meets Bagel一同合辦，並與本地交友配對公司HK Romance Dating作合作夥伴，於2月11日（星期日）在科學園舉行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/24/184913_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F24%2F184913_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2942173c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在起跑前，參加者需分組進行雙人熱身操，在專業運動員帶領下進行互動熱身。然後透過手帶配對分成2人一組，在五公里的賽道上的互遊戲站進行多個活動，拉近與心儀對象距離，而賽程中途，其中一位需戴上眼罩，在另一位跑手牽手引領下跑100米，考驗二人之間的合拍及信任度。 終點前更有石春路，參加者需一同牽手跑過終點完成的長跑，而情侶組完賽後更有機會獲得最合襯服裝獎 。而當中的活動環節更是以幫助弱勢社群作主題，邊跑步邊體驗當中的艱辛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/24/185110_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F24%2F185110_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b52f25e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/24/185122_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F24%2F185122_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=864a8997&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同場有不同咖啡專門店，各參加者可於賽前或賽後享受咖啡及認識身邊朋友。在運動前喝咖啡，更可促進身體消耗能量，加速脂肪燃燒。亦有大型互動遊戲、攤位遊戲、美食及飲品提供。<br />\n<br />\n於12月26日前報名此活動可享受早鳥優惠，單人收費為$280，雙人費用為$500；正價則單人$350，雙人$600。有興趣報名的朋友記得盡快報名<br />\n<br />\n報名:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ticketflap.com/zh/rundatefestival/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketflap.com%2Fzh%2Frundatefestival%2F&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=835c4a6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ticketflap.com/zh/rundatefestival/</a>"},{"pid":"686481a9cb4131a2ebf2dbeafceab98c92643eb8","tid":508533,"uid":116530,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T10:53:26.000Z","msg":"男女比例20:1"},{"pid":"85969efb4d3e7545c15316aa3ad94a573104db52","tid":508533,"uid":30123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T11:00:24.000Z","msg":"全男"},{"pid":"b414a5b3f459cb296c8458402bcf5e69cc511808","tid":508533,"uid":128441,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T11:10:14.000Z","msg":"香港大型嘻嘻號召活動"},{"pid":"1e84271250c7f9ae2a5049f7a7d275c67bad363b","tid":508533,"uid":21355,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T11:12:49.000Z","msg":"去格劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20ab044b9c98141e80ead38cda18b009e10404a0","tid":508533,"uid":28366,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T13:59:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5591e9c6435626cff205617d4d6d00b895df0be0","tid":508533,"uid":29523,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T14:05:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">報名此活動可享受早鳥優惠，單人收費為$280，雙人費用為$500；正價則單人$350，雙人$600。有興趣報名的朋友記得盡快報名</span></span><br />\n<br />\n好心啦，聖誕流流，又出黎呃鳩班毒撚錢，仲要收完錢，再叫成班毒撚鳩跑做撚埋你人肉佈景影相做宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"490de66c76c8822511e5f10efabda50a15ab55e9","tid":508533,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T14:05:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">報名此活動可享受早鳥優惠，單人收費為$280，雙人費用為$500；正價則單人$350，雙人$600。有興趣報名的朋友記得盡